Q1: Create a one-time thread job to find all text files (*.txt) on the filesystem.

A:

```powershell
Start-ThreadJob -ScriptBlock {
    Get-ChildItem -Path "C:\Users\deanschauer" -Filter *.txt -Recurse
}
```

