#Encountered ScriptBlock binding errors when attempting to pass commands directly to the -ScriptBlock parameter

#Learned that ScriptBlock commands must be enclosed in curly braces {}

#Initially attempted to use:

```powershell
-Include *.txt
```

#Observed that no results were returned when retrieving job output

#Reviewed Get-ChildItem filtering options

#Learned that -Filter provides a cleaner and more reliable method for locating specific file types

#Added -Recurse to search all subdirectories beneath the specified path

#Verified job creation using:

