Q2: You realize it would be helpful to identify all text files on some of your servers. How would you run the same command from task 1 on a group of remote computers?

A:

```powershell
Invoke-Command -ComputerName Server1, Server2, Server3 -ScriptBlock {
    Get-ChildItem -Path "C:\Users" -Filter *.txt -Recurse
}
```

